I rebuilt nnpack shared libraries and confirmed that it linked correctly against ATen.

Since I can't reproduce, let's do some remote debugging. Clear your build directory and rebuild ATen from scratch, with the following commands:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make VERBOSE=1

Post the full verbose log; I'm particularly interested in the linker command that is failing.
